Regression and Curve Fitting
This project explores nonlinear regression techniques by fitting exponential and power models to a given data set.
The Maple implementation computes the regression parameters, compares the resulting models graphically, and analyzes which function best represents the observed data.

The Maple source code is included in this folder. The accompanying PDF contains both the code and the generated graphs,
allowing the implementation and results to be viewed without downloading or executing the program.
